			<h2 class="section__title">WCAG 2.1 and APCA.</h2>
			<p class="section__lede">
				Live ratio, AA/AAA × normal/large/UI badges, and Andrew Somers'
				signed APCA Lc. Hit auto-fix to nudge the foreground until it
				clears your target ratio while preserving hue.
			</p>
		</div>
